00:02:37.610 --> 00:02:40.700
Now, Haywood's reference
to Fontenelle transpires

00:02:40.700 --> 00:02:44.710
within a an establish tradition
of figurative associations

00:02:44.710 --> 00:02:49.460
that couple sexual seductions
with scientific knowledge.

00:02:49.460 --> 00:02:54.360
Natural philosophy texts,
beginning with Francis Bacon,

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:56.750
